      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've totally babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. If you're looking for a ride that feels practically brand new without that dealership headache, you've found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
