    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine. The powerplant remains in peak operating condition, with the individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system functioning with factory precision. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been inspected and remains free of fatigue, while the suspension geometry retains its original compliance and sharp turn-in response. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly weighted clutch and a responsive variable M-differential lock for optimal power distribution. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the stainless steel exhaust system, exhibits no signs of thermal stress or corrosion. This is a true collector-grade specimen for those who prioritize mechanical purity and documented maintenance provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
